                      "order":  2,
                      "content":  {
                                      "title":  "Will â€” questions and negative",
                                      "body":  "Questions with WILL:\nâ€¢ Will you be at the office tomorrow?\nâ€¢ Will it rain this evening?\nâ€¢ Will she accept the offer?\n\nNegative â€” WON\u0027T:\nâ€¢ I won\u0027t be late, I promise.\nâ€¢ They won\u0027t finish by Friday at this rate.\nâ€¢ He won\u0027t tell you â€” he never talks about personal things.\n\nShall I / Shall we? (offers/suggestions, British English)\nâ€¢ Shall I open the window?\nâ€¢ Shall we order food?",
                                      "grammar_note":  "Question: Will + subject + base verb?\nNegative: won\u0027t / will not + base verb"
                                  }
                  },
